  "pokedexDescription": "It can't stand long periods of silence, so it often goes out of its way to be around others. In an attempt to keep people happy, it likes to put on grand and over-the-top performances to wow the audience. If it senses negative emotions like anger, jealousy, or annoyance, it adopts those emotions and retaliate with a flaming whip.",
